    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Key Points\n\n✅ All GHL interactions via HTTP\n✅ Full conversation history every time\n✅ GPT-5 can trigger handoff via function\n✅ Explicit routing (IF node)\n✅ 4x cheaper than MCP approach\n\n**Next Steps:**\n1. Add your full system prompt\n2. Configure GHL API credentials\n3. Test with real webhook data",
        "height": 284,
